{"tid":1441674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬仆街啲定政府仆街啲？","createTime":"2019-08-10T17:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:31:12.000Z","uid":197696,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0a98db3a437a079e7e77a00b4711819905b2ee6d","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"最近有小小感受<br />\n<br />\n睇見最近啲行動個目標都係撚狗為主。呢幾個星期手足四圍撚狗，成功撚狗的確大快人心，但同時有好多手足俾人拉咗。然後又聽見有人話啲狗係政府最後防線，只要啲狗收皮政府自然會出黎認輸。但又有人話應該對準返政權，毋忘五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n而加警犬日日開記招做小丑，清場做仆街。整場運動嘅輿論同注意都俾佢哋拎曬，政府就繼續唔聽我哋啲訴求同聲音。<br />\n<br />\n恕我無知一問，警犬的確係仆街，但點解唔推倒咗政權先再清算啲狗？狗係仆街但我哋唔可以忘記背後仲有個仲仆街嘅政府。最怕會撚狗撚到最後唔知自己做緊乜。"},{"pid":"d867db2851b79ee2c6f0f77f3c0339ffc47650d2","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:12:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"994cf916e354a90acd8079633df34627d3e04e57","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9197015e2d9e22f30a7648096f729ca08b72fb32","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:13:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6920ef0c182ceffdab948fd852c9caa02f4635cd","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"433f806e493d7d07315b15b99b88618bc01714c0","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c95db11b1c10624a553876eddf251580df2eee4e","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c53689cb43149fbff38c9a906fd13e5954ec23e","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6146c6f0dea5858e734b4f8fad18c1bae73a146c","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32b833f742fddc5120689b8ab284cdec1a60e1c9","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5aeaa9258899a837983e1a866989b3165bc780a7","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"312ca389405dc258de10e985ad4614f0eba00c99","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab737cadf8f140fcf2b1267b82bddf377cff1b77","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f696d56501813d1e4d3b85aa20fc0de927bb9d28","tid":1441674,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63cb70741531f0e870678839cd1313138d4e746","tid":1441674,"uid":57633,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"兩者係一體<br />\n咪浪費大家時間<br />\n請推有用post"},{"pid":"95da78d5e347243cab025e40c8f2acbbfe89f781","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f696d56501813d1e4d3b85aa20fc0de927bb9d28","tid":1441674,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e0439495282b4207321c6e41c96fac0c2a0d5c","tid":1441674,"uid":14422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"唔洗花時間分邊個仆街啲"},{"pid":"27680306e18272af9209e4e7f7db30ffd3e1ff38","tid":1441674,"uid":225409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:24:43.000Z","msg":"都係仆街 不用分那麼細"},{"pid":"d75b28445a6213f06cf669089449070aee7b9de5","tid":1441674,"uid":215044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"但係一日有犬係到幫政府做污糟野<br />\n你點推倒個政府?"},{"pid":"cbdd7489a4f2d08378fddb039c964a7f10fbce4f","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f63cb70741531f0e870678839cd1313138d4e746","tid":1441674,"uid":57633,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"兩者係一體<br />\n咪浪費大家時間<br />\n請推有用post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"係一體但應該對邊個位落手先最有效<br />\n啲狗每日出嚟拎曬我哋注意，有示威就做仆街<br />\n然後政府就繼續站喺高地睇我哋同啲狗對侍<br />\n咁睇落政府永遠都係贏家"},{"pid":"2a9ea068ca7153867391deae886bdcad5751d149","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d75b28445a6213f06cf669089449070aee7b9de5","tid":1441674,"uid":215044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"但係一日有犬係到幫政府做污糟野<br />\n你點推倒個政府?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:30:04.000Z","msg":"所以我就喺呢個迷思入面<br />\n到底點先可以推倒政府再清算黑警<br />\n我心入面有先後同主次之分<br />\n見解唔同屌細力啲"},{"pid":"d4d06b8254cd4422212d653ebffafbe0f8d18f40","tid":1441674,"uid":62032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d75b28445a6213f06cf669089449070aee7b9de5","tid":1441674,"uid":215044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"但係一日有犬係到幫政府做污糟野<br />\n你點推倒個政府?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"係試吓搵啲方法<br />\n可以唔需要同狗硬碰硬，直接同個政府玩<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋同狗打，一定係我哋比較傷</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段時間，全部受傷被捕嘅都係手足<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">啲狗人照打，狗糧照出8萬粒</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔硬碰硬</span></span>係指<br />\n好似去啲狗唔可以做嘢嘅場，做啲非衝擊行為<br />\n即係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">去機場和你飛輸出革命，塞爆個商場之類</span></span><br />\n真係拉咗好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d8a0aa82faa75e614bf7543bca9f4593df2cf7","tid":1441674,"uid":285466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a98db3a437a079e7e77a00b4711819905b2ee6d","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:10:45.000Z","msg":"最近有小小感受<br />\n<br />\n睇見最近啲行動個目標都係撚狗為主。呢幾個星期手足四圍撚狗，成功撚狗的確大快人心，但同時有好多手足俾人拉咗。然後又聽見有人話啲狗係政府最後防線，只要啲狗收皮政府自然會出黎認輸。但又有人話應該對準返政權，毋忘五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n而加警犬日日開記招做小丑，清場做仆街。整場運動嘅輿論同注意都俾佢哋拎曬，政府就繼續唔聽我哋啲訴求同聲音。<br />\n<br />\n恕我無知一問，警犬的確係仆街，但點解唔推倒咗政權先再清算啲狗？狗係仆街但我哋唔可以忘記背後仲有個仲仆街嘅政府。最怕會撚狗撚到最後唔知自己做緊乜。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:49:50.000Z","msg":"打和啦 super<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d21d4b23056c9766cb4cfc951a5138f77bb58f8","tid":1441674,"uid":94819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c0d60d12cfe9fb8c508b6c4d14fb30597f46101","tid":1441674,"uid":197696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4d06b8254cd4422212d653ebffafbe0f8d18f40","tid":1441674,"uid":62032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d75b28445a6213f06cf669089449070aee7b9de5","tid":1441674,"uid":215044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"但係一日有犬係到幫政府做污糟野<br />\n你點推倒個政府?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:43:44.000Z","msg":"係試吓搵啲方法<br />\n可以唔需要同狗硬碰硬，直接同個